Package com.google.cloud.bigtable.data.v2.stub.mutaterows Description

Implementation details for EnhancedBigtableStub.bulkMutateRowsCallable().

The implementation adapts gax's BatchingCallable to work with Bigtable's MutateRows RPC. There are 3 customizations that are necessary:

  • BulkMutationsUserFacingCallable: Wraps request and response protobufs.
  • BulkMutationsSpoolingCallable: The Bigtable protocol streams results from the mutations as they are applied. However gax's BatchingCallable is designed for UnaryCallables. This adapter spools the responses and presents the results as if they came from a UnaryCallable.
  • BulkMutateRowsBatchingDescriptor: Each entry can fail independently from the overall request. The descriptor splits the results for each entry and notifies the responsible issuer.

This package is considered an internal implementation detail and is not meant to be used by applications directly.
